<!DOCTYPE html><html><body>
<h2>Rental Cancellation Confirmed</h2>
<p>Hi <%= @member.firstname %>,</p>
<p>We've received your cancellation request for rental <strong><%= @rental.number %></strong>.</p>
<p>Since you indicated you have not yet vacated the space, your rental will remain active until <strong><%= @expiry %></strong>. Please ensure you have removed all belongings by that date.</p>
<p>No further charges will be made after your current rental period ends.</p>
<p>If you have any questions please contact us at contact@manchestermakerspace.org.</p>
<p>— Manchester Makerspace</p>
</body></html>
